overview: A material. A style. A purpose. A structure. The day. The night. The tragedy. The change. The pain. The monotony. A material. A style. A purpose. A structure. The day... The tragedy. The change... The monotony... The day and the night contrast in an orderly monotony of days. Something has changed, but everything has remained the same. A history of Autosilo Balestra.
title: RAW CONCRETE
